| Multi-module change                |         No |   Sometimes |        Yes |
| Multi-service change               |         No |          No |        Yes |
| Agent orchestration                |         No |          No |        Yes |
| Dynamic workflow engine            |         No |          No |        Yes |
| Requires execution plan            |         No |          No |        Yes |
